00:19:25,857 --> 00:19:29,536
We will still have a way to solve it

264
00:19:30,076 --> 00:19:33,231
But it is more energy consuming

265
00:19:35,116 --> 00:19:38,120
To fight with a smart woman.

266
00:19:39,613 --> 00:19:44,695
Therefore stupid but obedient women

267
00:19:45,132 --> 00:19:46,380
are the cutest

268
00:19:47,389 --> 00:19:51,715
But it is not definite that you will love cute women

269
00:19:52,949 --> 00:19:56,316
You are really a good partner to chat with

270
00:19:58,019 --> 00:20:00,710
Just take your time

271
00:20:01,058 --> 00:20:02,585
Since you like Concubinet Wan

272
00:20:02,634 --> 00:20:06,945
You can solve this in a short period of time

273
00:20:07,664 --> 00:20:10,667
Since Concubine Wan has prejudices with you

274
00:20:10,700 --> 00:20:13,289
Why don't you accommodate her

275
00:20:22,429 --> 00:20:23,266
Su Pei-Sheng

276
00:20:25,921 --> 00:20:26,916
Your Majesty

277
00:20:27,424 --> 00:20:28,675
You're still awake?

278
00:20:28,694 --> 00:20:30,255
Isn't it morning yet?

279
00:20:30,603 --> 00:20:31,757
It is almost morning

280
00:20:32,071 --> 00:20:34,034
It will be morning in four hours' time.

281
00:20:35,038 --> 00:20:35,748
I am going to sleep

282
00:20:39,431 --> 00:20:41,185
Extinguish two more candles

283
00:20:41,467 --> 00:20:42,073
Yes

284
00:20:46,554 --> 00:20:49,023
His Majesty is here

285
00:20:52,064 --> 00:20:54,073
Greetings your Majesty

286
00:20:54,432 --> 00:20:55,302
Please rise.

287
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:56,830
Thank you your Majesty

288
00:21:01,706 --> 00:21:03,538
Your majesty just finished your court hearings

289
00:21:03,596 --> 00:21:05,674
Is there any vexation?

290
00:21:07,663 --> 00:21:10,891
I have something to discuss with you

291
00:21:11,191 --> 00:21:13,715
Since you are all here, listen to me as well.

292
00:21:14,316 --> 00:21:18,955
This morning the Dzungaria sent people to propose marriage

293
00:21:19,277 --> 00:21:23,671
So that their lord can marry our princess

294
00:21:23,887 --> 00:21:25,426
and pacify the residents of Dzungaria

295
00:21:25,659 --> 00:21:28,371
It is common for the princess of our country to marry outsider

296
00:21:28,455 --> 00:21:32,099
We just need to pick a suitable girl from the palace

297
00:21:32,110 --> 00:21:34,391
And honor her as princess

298
00:21:34,711 --> 00:21:40,905
But the problem is they want a princess from the main royal family, not the branch family

299
00:21:41,147 --> 00:21:44,730
Dzungaria belongs to Qing dynasty, It is a small tribe at the boundry of our country

300
00:21:45,044 --> 00:21:48,555
It is already an honor that our princess will marry them

301
00:21:48,977 --> 00:21:52,143
Yet they want more and more and insist on a princess from the main royal family!

302
00:21:52,186 --> 00:21:54,231
They are really too much!

303
00:21:54,581 --> 00:21:56,946
Normally we only choose princesses from the branch family

304
00:21:57,060 --> 00:22:02,420
The only exception was when the previous emperor married his own daughter to Dzungaria

305
00:22:03,295 --> 00:22:05,669
That's why it is hard for me to reject

306
00:22:05,969 --> 00:22:07,572
As this example existed

307
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:13,238
Your Majesty, although Wen-Yi is your biological daughter, she is too young to marry!

308
00:22:13,539 --> 00:22:15,356
I won't be bothered by this

309
00:22:15,376 --> 00:22:18,856
If she is not underage

310
00:22:19,723 --> 00:22:23,828
You are clear about the condition in the government

311
00:22:24,228 --> 00:22:27,183
I have just come to the throne for about three years

312
00:22:27,699 --> 00:22:29,914
And conquered the northwest

313
00:22:30,826 --> 00:22:33,625
Dzungaria used to be violent

314
00:22:34,315 --> 00:22:36,791
We will have war again

315
00:22:36,847 --> 00:22:38,880
If this thing can't be solved properly

316
00:22:39,316 --> 00:22:42,465
We won't have enough supplies

317
00:22:42,900 --> 00:22:45,500
If we have war now

318
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:47,800
It is really a bad idea

319
00:22:47,810 --> 00:22:49,837
Your majesty is right

320
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:52,700
We have to look

321
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:56,900
at the big picture

322
00:22:57,400 --> 00:23:02,000
Approving the proposal is the only way

323
00:23:02,003 --> 00:23:07,043
It's just that my princess Wen-Yi is too young

324
00:23:07,108 --> 00:23:11,012
I can't find a suitable person

325
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:14,800
Dzungaria only wants the princess from the main family

326
00:23:14,812 --> 00:23:17,122
They didn't ask for your Majesty's biological daughters

327
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:18,300
Do you mean

328
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:22,000
The youngest daughter of the previous emperor, Princess Zhao-Gui is single

329
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:25,300
Still in puberty, she is the most suitable person.

330
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:29,600
But she is my youngest sister

331
00:23:29,700 --> 00:23:34,200
Your Majesty has constantly sacrificed himself for the country

332
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:38,000
So your sister should do the same.

333
00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:42,900
Moreover Princess Zhao-Gui's mother is only a Lady in the Previous Emperor's court.

334
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:48,100
Even if Your Majesty were to arrange a marriage for her in the future, you will only pick a officer from the governmen

335
00:23:48,155 --> 00:23:53,042
It will not be as honorable as marrying Dzungaria.

336
00:23:56,300 --> 00:23:58,200
Empress, you are right.

337
00:23:58,600 --> 00:24:01,600
She is my only single sister.

338
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:04,900
I must plan for her

339
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:07,000
On further reflection

340
00:24:07,600 --> 00:24:11,500
The Lord of Dzungaria is from a noble family.

341
00:24:11,800 --> 00:24:15,200
As Zhao-Gui is our only choice

342
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:18,600
Then I will let Empress prepare everything.

343
00:24:18,700 --> 00:24:21,000
She will marry Dzungaria ten days later.

344
00:24:21,100 --> 00:24:24,300
Yes, I will do my best.

345
00:24:24,400 --> 00:24:28,100
Since we are arranging her marriage

346
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:30,700
I will honor her as Princess Gu-Lun

347
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:33,000
So arrange the preparations according to this position

348
00:24:33,001 --> 00:24:34,312
Yes

349
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:39,300
It is might be easy to say the Imperial Household can handled the dowry.

350
00:24:39,325 --> 00:24:42,352
But there are difficult aspects too, we can't afford to make any mistake

351
00:24:42,402 --> 00:24:45,413
Or it will embarrass the Qing dynasty.

352
00:24:45,500 --> 00:24:48,400
Having too many people handling this may not be ideal, I think

353
00:24:48,600 --> 00:24:51,000
Sister Cao is very meticulous

354
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:54,100
why don't we ask her to help the princess to prepare?

355
00:24:55,400 --> 00:24:57,800
I really don't know anything about such matters

356
00:24:58,000 --> 00:25:01,000
I am afraid I will let Your Majesty's and Sister's good intentions down.

357
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:04,000
You are suited to these tasks.

358
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:08,000
The rest will be handled by the Empress.

359
00:25:08,100 --> 00:25:08,700
Yes.

360
00:25:08,700 --> 00:25:10,900
I have to leave now

361
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:13,300
Goodbye, Your Majesty

362
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:22,800
You did not say anything for a while but in the end you suggested that Lady Cao should handle the dowry.

363
00:25:22,900 --> 00:25:24,600
What are you thinking?

364
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:27,600
I did not say anything in the beginning because I don't approve of the marriage

365
00:25:27,610 --> 00:25:29,541
But I can't change it either

366
00:25:29,600 --> 00:25:31,300
I feel sad for Princess Zhao-Cui.

367
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:35,000
Yes, Dzungaria is a violent tribe.

368
00:25:35,041 --> 00:25:38,432
It is fine if she can marry a good man.

369
00:25:38,500 --> 00:25:43,500
But the Lord of Dzungaria is old, he is almost 60 years old.

370
00:25:44,700 --> 00:25:47,000
Poor Princess is only in her puberty.

371
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:50,900
The Lord is old enough to be her grandfather.

372
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:55,000
But His Majesty needs her to marry Dzungaria

373
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:58,200
She can't avoid

374
00:25:58,224 --> 00:26:00,456
this marriage.

375
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:03,800
Isn't Nian Gengyao a good warrior?

376
00:26:03,857 --> 00:26:08,996
Why don't His Majesty let him go conquer Dzungaria?

377
00:26:09,100 --> 00:26:11,300
Why do we have to send troops if the matter can be solved by a woman?

378
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:15,600
Nian Gengyao has great achievements in the military but if he loses, the price

379
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:17,400
would not be just a Princess.

380
00:26:17,700 --> 00:26:21,900
If he wins,, he will have more power and might threaten His Majesty's position.

381
00:26:22,100 --> 00:26:25,200
Therefore His Majesty has no other choice.

382
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:31,900
Did His Majesty look at you at all when he was here just now?

383
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:36,800
No, I am useless, I am unable to gain His Majesty's favour

384
00:26:36,808 --> 00:26:40,043
It is not that you are useless, it is Concubine Wan who is too capable.

385
00:26:40,100 --> 00:26:43,400
Without her, His Majesty was attentive to you.

386
00:26:43,423 --> 00:26:47,444
But now she is back, His Majesty could not even remember you.

387
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:51,300
Sister has been away from His Majesty for a while so it is normal for him to look for her now.

388
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,900
What about the future?

389
00:26:53,400 --> 00:26:58,600
Your days with His Majesty is not short either, do you still want him to care for you?

390
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:03,300
Yes, I await your Majesty's guidance.

391
00:27:04,600 --> 00:27:08,400
Concubine Wan is still powerful when she was not the beloved of His Majesty

392
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:11,500
Do you still remember Lady Chun?

393
00:27:12,600 --> 00:27:15,400
Being close to Concubine Wan and other consorts

394
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:17,600
is the long-term way

395
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:20,100
I understand.

396
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:37,200
Check

397
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:41,400
I lose.

398
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:45,700
Your Majesty has lost, so Your Majesty must stay here.

399
00:27:46,900 --> 00:27:49,900
You have been chasing me away for days.

400
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:53,200
Finally you are letting me stay.

401
00:27:53,600 --> 00:27:58,000
Since you like the House of Broken Jade so much, I will let you stay

402
00:27:58,100 --> 00:28:01,400
You stay here Your Majesty. I will go over to Lady Hui's place for the night.

403
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:06,400
Your Majesty lost the game and so you have to stay but I need not stay.

404
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:10,600
I have not fully recovered from my illness

405
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:14,100
Since Your Majesty wishes to stay here, I will have to go somewhere else.

406
00:28:17,500 --> 00:28:21,300
You are not well, you stay.

407
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:24,300
I am going back to the Hall of Mental Cultivation.

408
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:31,800
Goodbye, Your Majesty

409
00:28:42,500 --> 00:28:45,100
Your Ladyship, it is the fourth day

410
00:28:45,100 --> 00:28:47,100
you are still chasing away His Majesty

411
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:51,500
Not letting him stay. There are so many rumors as a result.

412
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:57,000
So what? I don't care about rumors.

413
00:28:57,800 --> 00:29:02,100
But isn't Your Ladyship worried that His Majesty may be so upset he will not return?

414
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:07,400
Did you hear the story of the wife of Emperor Wu of Han?

415
00:29:07,700 --> 00:29:11,200
Emperor Wu of Han loved Madam Li because of her beauty

416
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:13,800
And before Emperor Wu died, he wanted to see her for the last time

417
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:16,200
But she had covered her face.

418
00:29:16,207 --> 00:29:18,191
She did not allowed him to see her even when he was dead.

419
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:22,500
It is because she had become ugly

420
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:26,200
She was the nightmare of every woman in the palace.

421
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:31,100
The best thing is the thing that you have lost and cannot recover easily.

422
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:34,700
Her Ladyship keeps chasing His Majesty away

423
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:37,700
so as to entice him further.

424
00:29:38,300 --> 00:29:43,500
Yes, you are right.

425
00:29:43,600 --> 00:29:46,500
This is just a scheme.

426
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:50,500
But you should not overdo it.

427
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:54,900
Or your effort will be in vain

428
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:04,300
Princess is so pitiable. It is so quiet.

429
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:06,300
No one has come to her wedding ceremony.

430
00:30:06,600 --> 00:30:11,000
It is obvious her position is not important, His Majesty has never cared for his sister.

431
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:14,800
Morever marrying her to an outsider means they will never meet again.

432
00:30:14,900 --> 00:30:18,100
His Majesty has only one sister and he can bear to do so.

433
00:30:18,100 --> 00:30:20,000
Even if it is his biological daughter

434
00:30:20,007 --> 00:30:23,000
His Majesty will have no choice.

435
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:30,700
I wonder who will be next?

436
00:30:56,500 --> 00:30:59,200
Why did you not let me know you are here?

437
00:30:59,257 --> 00:31:01,536
It shows I have no manners

438
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:05,700
I just sent Princess Zhao-Gui and her retinue away

439
00:31:07,000 --> 00:31:09,900
I saw you sewing so seriously

440
00:31:09,900 --> 00:31:11,900
I did not want to disturb you

441
00:31:12,800 --> 00:31:16,300
I was just killing time

442
00:31:16,600 --> 00:31:18,900
Is the Princess fine?

443
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:21,900
She cried very sadly

444
00:31:22,300 --> 00:31:24,700
I did not want to part with her either.

445
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:28,000
So I came here.

446
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:31,400
What are you sewing?

447
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:34,700
I wanted to sew a sachet for Your Majesty

448
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:41,000
But I am slow, I have only just finished sewing the dragon,and have not decided what the color of the clouds should be.

449
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:43,300
Any colour will do

450
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:47,500
Your good intentions are more important.

451
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:51,900
Everything about Your Majesty must be perfect

452
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:56,000
Just like what you said, the sachet represents my good intentions.

453
00:31:56,006 --> 00:31:58,513
So I cannot take this lightly

454
00:31:58,800 --> 00:32:02,600
I like the light purple color of your clothes.

455
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:06,900
It matches the golden dragon.

456
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:11,100
Purple clouds and golden dragon

457
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:14,000
Indeed a really propitious sign.

458
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:19,400
When you finished sewing,

459
00:32:19,424 --> 00:32:24,001
I will carry the sachet on me every day

460
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:26,300
Never let it out of my sight.

461
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:28,000
Alright?

462
00:33:17,000 --> 00:33:18,700
Niang Niang

463
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:27,500
Is His Majesty staying at the House of Mental Cultivation today

464
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:30,000
or meeting Lady An?

465
00:33:34,700 --> 00:33:38,500
Or is he staying at the House of Broken Jade?

466
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:39,900
Yes

467
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:44,100
Did't you say that woman has been rejecting His Majesty?

468
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:46,200
Yes, I heard that

469
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:49,000
But now it seems she has allowed him to stay.

470
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:53,600
She is acting and scheming to seduce His Majesty

471
00:33:53,640 --> 00:33:57,077
Niang Niang, don't get angry, think of your health.

472
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:02,900
You have put in too much incense

473
00:34:03,000 --> 00:34:05,000
Making you cough.

474
00:34:05,100 --> 00:34:06,400
Is it a lot?

475
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:11,100
Why didn't I smell anything?

476
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:15,000
Why can't I smell anything?

477
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:19,000
Oh

478
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:25,000
His Majesty isn't here so the smell isn't here either.

479
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:30,900
Concubine Wan has recovered, she can serve His Majesty again.

480
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,900
I am happy to see that too.

481
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:34,700
Thank you, Empress

482
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:41,600
Your Majesty, Consort Nian is outside, she wants to greet you.

483
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:44,700
It is cold outside, tell her to go back.

484
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:46,500
She does not need to greet me.

485
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:52,200
Consort Nian knows Your Majesty does not want to see her so she just wish to come in and kowtow to you at a distance.

486
00:34:52,300 --> 00:34:55,100
Let her come in and kowtow a greeting then.

487
00:34:55,100 --> 00:35:00,000
It is almost at yearend, let her do this to fulfill her wish.

488
00:35:00,100 --> 00:35:01,800
Then she does not need to come anymore.

489
00:35:01,900 --> 00:35:03,200
Let her enter.

490
00:35:03,203 --> 00:35:03,971
Yes

491
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:10,300
His Majesty calls Consort Nian to enter.

492
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:21,600
Greeting Your Majesty

493
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:23,000
Please rise.

494
00:35:23,200 --> 00:35:24,800
Thank you, Your Majesty

495
00:35:28,600 --> 00:35:34,500
I dare not ask Your Majesty for forgiveness but I have copied many scriptures when I was alone.

496
00:35:34,511 --> 00:35:37,872
I have sent them to the temple for the monks to read

497
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:41,000
Hopefully it can bless Your Majesty.

498
00:35:41,700 --> 00:35:45,800
I understand your good intentions. You can go back.

499
00:35:48,600 --> 00:35:50,000
Yes

500
00:35:58,200 --> 00:36:00,600
Concubine Wan is here too.

501
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:03,600
So many people

502
00:36:09,700 --> 00:36:12,200
I will leave first.

503
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:16,200
The weather is cold. Continue with the copying of the scriptures when spring comes.

504
00:36:19,395 --> 00:36:21,045
Yes

505
00:36:21,600 --> 00:36:27,700
You look good in purple yesterday, why don't you let the Imperial Household make more purple clothes for you?

506
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:30,600
Thank you, Your Majesty.

507
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:35,300
Sister, you finally got what you wanted

508
00:36:35,334 --> 00:36:37,513
I was really worried about you.

509
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:40,000
Sister is too kind.

510
00:36:40,100 --> 00:36:43,300
If you worry about me, come visit me often then.

511
00:36:43,308 --> 00:36:44,985
That's true.

512
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:48,100
When Concubine Wan is sick, His Majesty will look for you

513
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:52,500
Where would you have the time to visit your sister?

514
00:37:05,700 --> 00:37:08,000
What are you looking at?

515
00:37:08,400 --> 00:37:11,900
I was just thinking the year is ending soon.

516
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:15,000
If your Majesty can spend more time with Princess Wen-yi

517
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,600
she will be very happy

518
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:26,800
According to today's situation, although His Majesty did not pardon Consort Nian,

519
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:29,000
He did not punish her heavily either.

520
00:37:29,009 --> 00:37:32,362
She still has the chance to come back

521
00:37:32,500 --> 00:37:35,200
I knew that when I lost my baby

522
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:38,200
As long as Nian Genyao is in power, the Nian's family will not fall

523
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:41,100
No matter what Consort Nian does

524
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:44,200
His Majesty will not and dare not kill her.

