00:37:47,553 --> 00:37:50,980
His Majesty has no choice but to bear it.

527
00:37:50,984 --> 00:37:52,962
I don't understand all this

528
00:37:52,969 --> 00:37:56,493
But what is going on between you and Ling-Rong?

529
00:37:56,501 --> 00:37:59,382
I feel that both of you are not as close as before

530
00:37:59,783 --> 00:38:03,422
That's because we hardly meet now

531
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:09,000
If it is because of His Majesty, it is not worth it.

532
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:13,100
I saw that she seems to be trying to accommodate you today.

533
00:38:13,600 --> 00:38:16,000
Is it worth it?

534
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:23,900
Ling-Rong is very good at sussing out the situation.

535
00:38:24,300 --> 00:38:28,700
We will know the person's true nature after some time

536
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:34,000
If it is because of His Majesty, it is not worth it

537
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:37,600
But if it is for some other reason, you have to sort it out then.

538
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:42,600
The three of us came to the palace together, to be where we are today, it has not been easy.

539
00:38:42,700 --> 00:38:47,400
If she has done anything wrong, if we can compromise, we should.

540
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:51,400
Luckily Sister still treats me as before.

541
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:56,400
