543
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:08,200
Ji-Xi, let's go to the Imperial Garden for a walk.

544
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:10,700
Huan-Bi, you go back first.

545
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:27,200
I rarely meet both of you.

546
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:30,000
I was just thinking the snowy landscape is so pretty

547
00:39:30,100 --> 00:39:32,500
it is sad to enjoy it alone.

548
00:39:32,900 --> 00:39:38,700
It would be better to enjoy the scene with both of you.

549
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:42,300
I was about to go see Wen-yi but as I have not seen you for a while, i will remain.

550
00:39:42,300 --> 00:39:46,900
